The Vim Way chap 1

1) Our work is repetitive by nature.
2) the dot command is our starting point. This seemingly simple command is the most versatile tool in the box, and
understand it is the first step toward vim mastery.

The dot command lets us repeat the last change. It is the most powerful and versatile command in vim.

>G command to increase the indentation form the current line Until the end of the file.

We can think of . command as being a miniature macro, or a "micro".

